Only reference local files (no http URLs) so that the documents can be
typeset without network access or when xml.resource.org is down.

For RFC XYZ, use this command to fetch its contents into this
directory:

 curl -O http://xml2rfc.tools.ietf.org/public/rfc/bibxml/reference.RFC.XYZ.xml

For Internet-Drafts, use this command to fetch official bibliographic
references:

 curl -O http://xml2rfc.tools.ietf.org/public/rfc/bibxml3/reference.I-D.XYZ.xml

For other references (academic publications, etc.), create the reference
file by hand.
